        Form 6 Agency Agreement in Queensland: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Before you sign a Form 6, understand what you're agreeing to. Here's a plain-English guide to the document that authorises your agent to sell your property in Queensland.
      </p>
